high_descs: Turn around and exit the room, then go to the room across you; upon entering the room, walk toward the bed, which is on your right side; there is a lettuce on the bed, face the bed.
Pick up the ladle behind the lettuce on the bed.
Turn left and walk toward the drawer by bed.
Open the top drawer of the nightstand, put the ladle in the drawer while keeping the bowl part of the ladle toward the opening; close the drawer when done.
Turn around to exit the room, then go to the bathroom across you; upon entering the room, walk toward the toilet straight ahead.
Pick up the ladle on the toilet.
Turn around to exit the bathroom and go to the room across you; upon entering the room, walk toward the drawer which is slightly on your right by the wall and bed.
Open the top drawer of the nightstand, put the ladle in the drawer while keeping the bowl part of the ladle in an opposite direction to that of the other ladle ; close the drawer when done.
anns.task_desc: Store two Ladles in Drawer of nightstand.
